{"tid":1827902,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"醫管局表示再多4宗曾訪武漢後發燒或呼吸道感染個案","createTime":"2020-01-17T10:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T01:58:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2749da3afd0412f370720c2ab9e44bc689bd77f7","tid":1827902,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:24:05.000Z","msg":"醫管局表示，截至中午12時，本港公立醫院過去24小時，再接收多4宗曾到武漢，出現發燒、呼吸道感染或肺炎徵狀的個案。他們年齡介乎24至43歲，分別入住瑪嘉烈、瑪麗及伊利沙伯醫院。<br />\n<br />\n病人樣本已送交衞生署化驗，在所有呈報個案中，6人仍然留院接受隔離，全部情況穩定。公立醫院至今未有確診感染新型冠狀病毒個案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503400-20200117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503400-20200117.htm&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=ef65bc5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503400-20200117.htm&h=a87090fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503400-20200117.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c9d57a778c74d74d1e86a1f1321af57702400c87","tid":1827902,"uid":281388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0fd191fdf49413660fa1f9d805307517ac9165","tid":1827902,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccb413c37ff5794c53a25e05027b706b6bdbc01","tid":1827902,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"但0確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9af4616d191ec8464b5fa7d086f849a9cd21d5d","tid":1827902,"uid":258687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"屌那星 未到春運就咁鳩樣<br />\n<br />\n一到春運咪仆直？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj